Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.09,0:00:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't look anything like the genuine piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it was right of me to have done some practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of attempting on the genuine piece right from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans aren't suitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll rot right away and become moldy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I plaster and let them dry, they lose more and more of their feminine essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ought to collect more materials for my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To obtain the girl who resembles the genuine piece.
