Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there's a man carrying\Na huge black egg with a doll inside of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.13,0:01:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, the doll had no arms or legs,\Nbecause there's no way they could fit it inside the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since the doll closely resembles a human being,\Nyou would think it could've been a corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take a closer look...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see that it's neither a doll nor a corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a girl with no arms or legs living\Ninside the shell of a black egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:02:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If ever you encounter that man, you ought\Nto tell him that you're not the “Girl in the Shell.”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Otherwise, you'll trade places with the girl inside the black shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:13.89,Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}Episode 2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:17.40,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H280D04&\bord0.5\fs75\3c&H854228&\b1\move(958,611,923,611,0,3500)}Tokisaka{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't informed the school about it yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But apparently, there are students\Nwho haven't returned home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that makes her the fourth victim, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to your help, we were able to identify the victim easily today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, who the funk that it'd turn out to be\Nfour students in a row from the same academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we can consider this a coincidence any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.47,0:02:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Was it too hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, this is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like this is orange juice, compared to\Nthe boiling water we'll make the culprit drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is the Tokisaka Residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like school's been canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have much of a choice with the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The higher-ups still haven't been informed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About all the victims who everyone's\Nbeen fussing about, went to the same academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if the culprit is doing a thorough check on the students,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the schoolgirls aren't necessarily safe\Neven if they're not going to the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the academy requires students to wear their uniforms off-campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a good chance for the culprit\Nto take note of them if they're wandering around alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Goddamn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what's going on in that damn culprit's mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't give a damn where he dumps the limbs,\Nyet we can't even find the bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's related to his objective...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something he wants us to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be necrophilia?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be easy to understand if that were the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kuchiki called just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Touko did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she didn't have to speak to you directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, she left you a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:07.80,Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinzou Mamiya Exhibit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kept you waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got here myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there's still time to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I apologize for making come all the way out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's move on to your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I wouldn't call it an official report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you want to look at some paintings while we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear what you have to say, Mr. Detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't feel like going to your office or a café.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found out several things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I start?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be conserved about the fact\Nthat I'm not the real daughter of the Kuchiki family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Checking my family registration is not that big of a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just... I haven't informed my mother\Nand everyone else that I do know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also the fact that before she adopted you,\Nyou used to live in Kurashiki, Okayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I discovered that your biological mother's\Nname is Misa Nakahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found out that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set a thief to catch a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just say I used to have a lot of contacts\Nin the bureaucratic offices back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I was right about you, Mr. Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, we were fortunate that there were still\Nofficial records available, despite the chaos after the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:05:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all that I've found so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could easily find more if I talk\Nto your current family members.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd... prefer you not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not remember what my birth parents look like,\Nbut my foster mother is like a real mother to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll have to go to Kurashiki to investigate\Nmore about this Misa Nakahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I don't have to time to leave town at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it about that case?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but people's lives are at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in that much of a rush anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, when you said\Nyou wanted me to find the real you, you meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finding your real parents to clarify your true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you really want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That may probably be some of my reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:07:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not exactly sure what I really want to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's what I want you to find, Mr. Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.85,0:07:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko tells me that I'm a level-headed person,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth is I don't know who I am or where I stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an fleeting existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I see appears vague,\Nas if they're shrouded in mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never consider anything I see beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you still paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I paint is neither a portrait nor a landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I paint is what's within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, that's why I can't manage to finish any of my pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for someone who can't see the beauty in things,\Nyou seem rather attracted to Shinzou Mamiya's paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:08:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see the darkness in Shinzou Mamiya's paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see the beauty in things,\Nbut I do see the darkness within.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What makes a colorful landscape beautiful is the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness is not vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That darkness lies within both you and I, Mr. Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart is shrouded in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there's still light within the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's may be faint,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it still shines upon my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'm on fire, and it hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for this painting,\NI can see the same darkness that resides within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Girl in the Shell.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I learned about this painting,\Nit made me decide to seek out who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to make things clear to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the “Girl in the Shell” and I are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to look at the “Girl in the Shell.”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have guessed that I'd meet you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko, why's this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember?\NHe's a Detective Reiji Tokisaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko, why are you with someone like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little rendezvous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko, don't be fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't be alone with a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The relationship me and Mr. Detective\Nhave is nothing indecent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He would never deceive me.{Well, not yet.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you to make excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What ever happened to the usual Touko that I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Touko I know is refined and beautiful like this painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to shine and be more radiant than anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This painting isn't radiant at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't compare me\Nwith the “Girl in the Shell” like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since Touko met you,\Nshe's been acting stranger and stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko, you should stop hanging out with this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko, Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Observe silence within the art museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stella...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
