Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.07,0:10:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasup?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just you, Dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukari isn't here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to talk to you today, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, quit calling me Dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here for another interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's half of the reason why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective, you're investigating\Nthe mutilation case everyone's talking about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukarin told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect Yukari to be such a blabbermouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I could help out in the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what could a schoolgirl possibly do anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate the great Tsuzuriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I came bearing some vital information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:15.07,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HA9A9A9&\fs60\frx4\fry2\frz344.193\pos(864,618)}Shell of \NSheol
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:15.19,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HA9A9A9&\fs60\frx4\fry2\frz344.193\pos(846,514)}Shell of \NSheol
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.53,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HA9A9A9&\fs60\frz343\frx4\fry2\pos(826,432)}Shell of \NSheol
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Your novel or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll bring mine next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's written by Shin Katsuragi, “Shell of Sheol.”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:28.03,Novel Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Shell of Sheol\Nby Shin Katsuragi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.03,0:11:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a story about a boy who loses his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of copying what his mother look like,\Nhe meets a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and chops off a her arms and legs, or so the story goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was his mother a paraplegic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He never mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, doesn't this look similar to the case?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably some coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely a connection!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer might have read this novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:11:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin Katsuragi himself might be behind all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're reading way too much into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I hate writers.{That's why I hate the editor of JPz Records.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way the culprit would write anything\Nrelated to his crimes, just for the world to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, there's a high possibility the culprit\Nwill target a schoolgirl from Ouba Girls Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep a low profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I'll investigate about it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Investigate? How are you going to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'd do more interviews!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I already got Mr. Katsuragi address\Nthrough my connections from the publisher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I'll get nervous meeting Katsuragi,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want you to tag along, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're a diehard Shin Katsuragi fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You just want to meet\Nyour favorite authors, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective, you're being such a meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait up, Dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit calling me Dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time messing around with schoolgirls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Shell of Sheol,” huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:13.12,Novel Page1,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy's mother\Nwas very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:18.05,Novel Page2,,0000,0000,0000,,She was inside\Nthe black shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:22.94,Default (Thinking),,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.36,Default (Thinking),,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:28.45,Default (Thinking),,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}No matter how similar they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten rather big now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, for a police officer, you lack decency.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a diligent person at work,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I got to let loose when I'm at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've cleaned it a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind wrapping it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't hold it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, you're still hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you still keep up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't believe something this big can fit inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Babies come out from there too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if ever we decide to have a baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind making mine wider?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji, it really is too big!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Yukiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting any wider?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But it f-feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukari will hear us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had a long day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sleeping like a log.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, moan all you want, she won't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji! Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji, oh, Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That... felt great...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko, let's settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm flattered, Mr. Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really protect me forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Where's Yukiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised you'd protect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sincere apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, something terrible happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Tsuzuriko didn't come home last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look around and search for her too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Yukari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not safe for Ouba Girls Academy students\Nto wonder alone in this current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call Uozumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the police handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the police won't take a missing girl lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:50.41,Default (Thinking),,0000,0000,0000,,“Shell of Sheol.”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.75,Default (Thinking),,0000,0000,0000,,Shin Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:54.92,Novel Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Shell of Sheol\Nby Shin Katsuragi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:20:01.16,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H494543&\frx318\fry354\fs60\frz346\pos(491,428)}Investigations Department
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:19:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Reiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's freaking early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another schoolgirl is missing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, there's something I want you to look into right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A novelist by the name of Shin Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a high possibility that he's involved in the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that guy you wanted me to look into...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin Katsuragi is just a pen name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His real name is Shinji Mamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By any chance, is he related to Shinzou Mamiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's his son or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But apparently, the public is unaware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, his workplace is at Shimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be a cottage he inherited from his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Shimo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did most of the crimes take place around that area?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's the perpetrator?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything reckless before we get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuzuriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuzuriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Like hell I'll wait for Uozumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuzuriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The “Girl in the Shell...”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:49.22,Default (Thinking),,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it's because of the police's sirens, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:50.71,Default (Thinking),,0000,0000,0000,,Shin Katsuragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:53.41,Default (Thinking),,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji Mamiya never came back to the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.09,0:21:55.30,Default (Thinking),,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:21:59.41,Default (Thinking),,0000,0000,0000,,We've placed a warrant for his arrest\Nfor the serial killings spree case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:06.43,Default (Thinking),,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, the whereabouts\Nof Shinji Mamiya remained a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard word...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what happened to Miss Yosomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.46,0:22:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had paid more attention to her seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:58.31,Default (Dead Version),,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)}Mr. Tokisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.70,0:23:02.43,Default (Dead Version),,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Mr. Tokisaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Mr. Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.02,0:23:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Mr. Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko, don't you ever leave my sight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.26,0:23:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't turn into the “Girl in the Shell,” right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.49,0:23:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Girl in the Shell?”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and find the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.92,0:23:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll wrinkle my uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.11,0:24:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.82,0:24:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.66,0:24:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.42,0:24:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.89,0:24:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.66,0:24:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.42,0:24:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to say those out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.93,0:24:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.34,0:24:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.25,0:25:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can... feel you... so much of you...\Ninside me, Mr. Detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.25,0:25:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko, is it all right if I move faster inside of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.50,0:25:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.42,0:25:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it however you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.76,0:25:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels better for men to do it this way, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.53,0:26:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.73,0:26:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.44,0:26:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Detective, I can feel it deep inside,\Nthroughout my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.72,0:26:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.78,0:26:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind's going blank!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.63,0:26:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.17,0:26:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.16,0:26:49.04,Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted: Shinji Mamiya
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.04,0:26:52.73,Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted: Shinji Mamiya
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.04,0:26:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone has information regarding to the\Nphotographed man, please report to us immediately.\N - Investigations Department
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.26,0:27:18.97,English Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,The shivering wind passes like a stroke on my cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.97,0:27:24.12,English Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a baby rebelling against the silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.12,0:27:28.07,English Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,It held tight to its embrace,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.07,0:27:33.76,English Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,Although the cage simply crumbled away.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.23,0:27:41.28,English Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,Transcending the confined time and space,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.28,0:27:46.20,English Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,The Azure Bird revealed a sign from the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.20,0:27:51.08,English Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the darkside of the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.08,0:27:55.56,English Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.56,0:27:59.87,English Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,Through a waning fissure,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.87,0:28:05.45,English Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a waving tapestry,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.45,0:28:10.26,English Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,I conceal a voiceless shout
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.26,0:28:14.72,English Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,Locked within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.72,0:28:20.40,English Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,My outstretched hands slip away,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.40,0:28:24.78,English Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet my memories can't recall a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.78,0:28:30.21,English Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,This crude body lost in the midst of doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.21,0:28:40.81,English Translation,,0000,0000,0000,,Struggles while drifting with a lingering miracle.
